approach :- Two pointer approach

formula :- area = base * min of two lines
		
		area => kitna pani store hoga
		base => dono lines ke beech kina gap h
	min of lines => choti line jitna hi pani store hoga.

-> left & right 2 pointer lenge ( left < right )
-> starting ke liye base => array_length-1 hoga kyoki dono lines left-most & right-most h

-> area find krenge left & right index ke liye
-> curr. area ko max-area ( res ) se compare krenge
-> jo line choti hogi uska index+1 kr denge

-> base-1 kr denge kyoki line km hone pe unke beech ka space bhi km hoga 

